♪ Is love alive? ♪

1:13:07.482 --> 1:13:08.517
♪ ♪

1:13:08.585 --> 1:13:10.068
♪ Is love alive? ♪

1:13:10.137 --> 1:13:12.862
- ♪ Is love alive?
both: Is love alive? ♪

